BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Run Apple Script (enter directly as text)
BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: if application "Safari" is running then	tell application "Safari"		repeat with t in tabs of windows			tell t				if URL starts with "http://www.youtube.com/watch" or URL starts with "https://www.youtube.com/watch" then					return text 1 thru -11 of (name of t as text)				end if			end tell		end repeat	end tellend ifreturn ""
